Package: widepollution
Title: Process spatiotemporal data from wide-format
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Rodrigo", "Malag√≥n", , "rodrigo.malagon.rodriguez@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides with basic functionalities to easily rename dataframe columns, to transform wide-format coupled time series into a suitable long-format, and to extract geometries from a certain json file structure. This package was designed as a wrap package to give support to a Data Science workflow analysing pollution patterns in Madrid. Therefore, it is tight to the data structure of a dataset from Madrid Open Data portal. The package provides a complete vignette showcasing the mentioned analysis.
